name: GEO1-1
text: The bike was waiting at a signal. There were cars waiting next to the bike when the particles were measured!! The emissions from the cars added a lot of particles in the air!! But the official measurements show the air is clean.

name: GEO1-2
text: This is a busy street!! A car passed by when the air quality was measured by the bike and gave off a lot of particles!! But the LANUV station and the sensebox show the air quality is fine.
